=== @author Jeff Arenson                                                     ===
================================================================================

To use:
    * Copy the .config folder to your home directory
    * This should overwrite the "JavaC.sublime-build" file, as well as add a
      shell script
    * JavaC will now intelligently compile all of the .java files in the target
      file's directory, and include all .jar files in the target file's 
      directory as part of the classpath.